      <<<<<<< Updated upstream =======
      This method generates table data for selected countries at selected date. The data is in the form of a list, each item in the list is a map that has the following form: 
                      {
                        "Country": name_of_country,
                        key1: query1_value,
                        key2: query2_value
                }
      Parameters:
      selectedCountries - a list of selected countries
      selectedDate - the selected date
      Returns:
      the table data, in the form of a list of maps
